          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你哪里说的是什么“迎接”二字，分明是前来捉拿孤家。杜茂吓，杜茂！想当"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "年孤家因你武艺超群，人才出众，曾将大队人马，交付你执掌，你就该一秉忠"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "心扶保孤家，才是正理。怎么你听信那妖道邓禹的谣言，私自带兵投降刘秀，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贪图富贵，负义忘恩，反敢前来拿我。有道是：飞鸟尽，良弓藏；狡兔死，走"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "狗烹；敌国破，谋臣亡吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "见杜茂把我的牙关咬坏，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "叫一声无义人细听开怀："
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "到如今降他人所为何来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是何人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想孤家相待你恩情似海"
        },
        {
          "character": "岑彭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣岑彭见驾。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岑彭，你也是前来捉拿孤家的么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "岑彭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣不敢，特地前来接驾。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想当初甲子之年曾开科场，你与马武二人技艺相同，那时孤家中了你的相貌，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不中马武的才能，不想他一怒，就在长安城外题下反诗，蛊惑黎民，险些成了"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大事。你不知以恩报德，反降他人，你的天良何在？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "小岑彭你不必巧言遮盖，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "曾记得甲子年把科场来开。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "弃了那马子章栋梁之才。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "你竟敢放大胆来到云台。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是何人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "中了你相貌好，格外优待"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "又谁知到如今良心改坏"
        },
        {
          "character": "邳彤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣邳彤前来接驾。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "邳彤，怎么你也降顺刘秀了？我且问你，大元帅他往哪里去了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "邳彤",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大元帅他战死疆场了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，不好了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "听说是战死了大元帅，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "我心中好一似刀来裁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "哪怕那汉兵将到此来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "眼前若有苏献在"
        },
        {
          "character": "马武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姚仁兄，你看他三人俱作过王莽的臣子，断断不能动手捉拿于他，待我二人进"
        },
        {
          "character": "马武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "观将他拿下便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "外面二人是谁？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜茂、岑彭、邳彤",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "乃是姚期、马武二人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你待怎讲？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜茂、岑彭、邳彤",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "姚期、马武二人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此二人乃是孤家冤家对头，今日到来，我命休矣！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "听说是姚期、马子章，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "倒叫孤家无主张。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "看起来我性命休定丧无常。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "他二人与孤家夙有冤枉"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "马武"
        },
        {
          "character": "姚期",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我等打进去！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（马武、姚期同拿王莽，同下，杜茂、岑彭、邳彤同下。）"
        }
      ],
