    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "刘秀",
        "四龙套",
        "岑彭",
        "探马",
        "杜茂",
        "王莽",
        "邳彤",
        "马武"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、四太监、刘秀、邓禹同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "云台观内捉王莽，且听探马报端详。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（探马上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "探马",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启主公：王莽拿到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将王莽绑至法场。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，带马。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘秀、邓禹、四龙套、四太监同大转场。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将王莽押上来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四龙套",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将王莽押上来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王莽 （内西皮导板） 八月十五把寿拜，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四刀手押王莽同上。姚期、马武、杜茂、岑彭、邳彤同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "满朝中的文武拜金阶。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "稳坐龙台称孤的心怀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "以谁知白水村出了个妖人刘秀，又报仇来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "事到临头我悔也悔不来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，御外男，愚外公这厢有礼了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三杯药酒把平帝爷害"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "实指望汉家绝了后代"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "而如今身捆铁索法场外"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，看酒祭奠。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖吹打〗。刘秀、杜茂、岑彭、邳彤同行礼，邓禹、姚期、马武同站。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，御外男，这千不是万不是乃是孤一时的糊涂，虽然作了一十八载的江山，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "并不曾残害过刘氏子孙。今日你已身登大宝，纵然将孤杀死，于你又有何益？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "望祈你念这甥舅之亲，将我饶恕，放我一条老命，孤就在这云台观内悟道参禅，"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "修真养性，不修今生，我还要修修来世。话已讲明，这杀也在你，不杀也在"
        },
        {
          "character": "王莽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看王莽在此苦苦哀求，泪如泉涌，小王意欲念在甥舅亲情，赦他一条性命，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不知列位意下如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杜茂、岑彭、邳彤",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但凭主公。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（邓禹看马武、姚期。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "马武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住！主公今日也说拿王莽，明日也说拿王莽，今将王莽拿到，你又要念什么"
        },
        {
          "character": "马武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "甥舅之情。他当年谋害平帝之时，怎么就不念这翁婿之意么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个……就请将军将他斩首。"
        },
        {
          "character": "马武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令！"
        },
        {
          "character": "马武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，击鼓。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。蟒形上，小童上，绳缚蟒形同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "光禄寺排宴，与众将军贺功。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
